From cac985cd669d6a84b1c3ddaa1d06ea8eed689f8f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jiansong Chen <Jiansong.Chen@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2020 18:42:04 +0800
Subject: drm/amdgpu: enable athub/mmhub PG for navy_flounder
Git-commit: 47fc894a8711e9cc22bc3c508d15415c0b191480
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

Enable athub/mmhub PG by setting the corresponding flags.
Actually the enablement is exercised by PMFW.

Signed-off-by: Jiansong Chen <Jiansong.Chen@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Kenneth Feng <kenneth.feng@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
index dc4c360e14b8..2f7fc9a5beed 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
@@ -786,7 +786,9 @@ static int nv_common_early_init(void *handle)
 			AMD_CG_SUPPORT_JPEG_MGCG;
 		adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN |
 			AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN_DPG |
-			AMD_PG_SUPPORT_JPEG;
+			AMD_PG_SUPPORT_JPEG |
+			AMD_PG_SUPPORT_ATHUB |
+			AMD_PG_SUPPORT_MMHUB;
 		adev->external_rev_id = adev->rev_id + 0x32;
 		break;
 
